original_title: 女子アナ訓練室 【別称:催●ルーム】
overview: A rookie female announcer who belongs to Hana's announcement club, who receives the eyes of envy. She expresses her honest attitude and words of gratitude without any doubts about her senior boy Anna's kind guidance [event]. The owner of a serious and not shy personality was a rare test subject who demonstrated various event adaptability during vocal practice, event photography, dry rehearsal, and location meetings.
title: Hypnotism Room - Female News Anchor Training Room... Kanna Misaki
